            <h2 style="text-align: center;">Extra Long Bedding 101</h2>
            <div class="shortcode-accordion">
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h3 class="accordion__title js-title js-title-iconed icon-class-goes-here">How long is an Extra Long Twin bed?<span class="open-close"><i class="icons8-multiply"></i></span></h3><div class="accordion__copy js-copy" style="display: none;">Twin extra long mattresses are most commonly referred to as Twin XL. The “XL” stands for extra long. The dimensions of twin extra long beds are 39 inches wide by 80 inches long. This means that twin extra long mattresses measure 5 inches longer than a standard Twin mattress. <a href="{{ shop.url }}/product-category/shop/twin-xl/">Shop Twin XL bedding now</a>.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h3 class="accordion__title js-title js-title-iconed icon-class-goes-here">What are the dimensions of a Full Extra Long mattress?<span class="open-close"><i class="icons8-multiply"></i></span></h3>
