                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h3 class="accordion__title js-title js-title-iconed icon-class-goes-here">Where are Twin Extra Long beds commonly used?<span class="open-close"><i class="icons8-multiply"></i></span></h3>
                    <div class="accordion__copy js-copy" style="display: none;">Twin Extra Long is the bedding and sheet size for Twin XL beds. Twin Extra Long bedding is necessary for dorm room living at most American colleges. Extra long beds can be difficult to shop for. Luckily, TwinXL.com has all of your college bedding essentials in one spot to make dorm room shopping quick, easy and affordable.</div>
