                    <div class="accordion__copy js-copy" style="display: none;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Microfiber is not graded in thread count. Microfiber fabric threads are much finer than cotton fiber threads, which would put microfiber thread count over 1200. This uneven comparison is why microfiber is instead graded by GSM (grams per square meter). Our microfiber fabric is a premium heavy weight fabric that has been double brushed for softness.</span></div>
